addr="erct-001I">proposition</fr:link>, so it suffices by the induction principle for <fr:link
href="erct-0028.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-0028">propositional truncation</fr:link> to observe that the <fr:link
href="erct-001Q.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-001Q">fiber</fr:link> is <fr:em>inhabited</fr:em> because <fr:tex>f</fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="erct-0029.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-0029">surjective</fr:link>.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
